{"tid":507863,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[成日都美斯C朗]有冇人好鐘意恩尼斯達呢位球員?","createTime":"2017-12-23T16:14:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-24T10:03:58.000Z","uid":120852,"like":87,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"5dffcee44962b4c5f51f3f643eeacd19ddaa99d6","tid":507863,"uid":120852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T16:14:18.000Z","msg":"由雙核時期已經好鐘意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n傳扭射分波護波樣樣有呢D招牌野唔駛講 剩係岩岩個場都見到佢雖然老左 視野同傳送仍然係頂級 70分鐘個下防守再幾下傳球策動番反攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢可能唔係最搶眼個堆 但佢作為一個球員真係好值得尊重個type出哂名好球品<br />\n佢亦都係歷史上係除左老馬同細哨以外唯一係打吡作客得到日日互屌既死敵皇馬球迷掌聲既人<br />\n好波仲要嬴得世仇對手既尊重真係唔係一件易事<br />\n<br />\n附送小白拎豬肉獎link<br />\n恩尼斯達，名符其實的「君子球員」<br />\n<a href=\"http://football.fanpiece.com/extra-time/%E6%81%A9%E5%B0%BC%E6%96%AF%E9%81%94-%E5%90%8D%E7%AC%A6%E5%85%B6%E5%AF%A6%E7%9A%84-%E5%90%9B%E5%AD%90%E7%90%83%E5%93%A1-c1264833.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffootball.fanpiece.com%2Fextra-time%2F%25E6%2581%25A9%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E6%2596%25AF%25E9%2581%2594-%25E5%2590%258D%25E7%25AC%25A6%25E5%2585%25B6%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E7%259A%2584-%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%2590%2583%25E5%2593%25A1-c1264833.html&d=YOYowMKT4GHpmLnXTDE8RhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=e5dfb4fc\" target=\"_blank\">http://football.fanpiece.com/extra-time/%E6%81%A9%E5%B0%BC%E6%96%AF%E9%81%94-%E5%90%8D%E7%AC%A6%E5%85%B6%E5%AF%A6%E7%9A%84-%E5%90%9B%E5%AD%90%E7%90%83%E5%93%A1-c1264833.html</a><br />\n恩尼斯達在過去一年的各項賽事中，沒有領過一張黃牌或紅牌，甚至被吹罰的過火動作也極少。事實上，他征戰沙場十多年，超過七百場比賽，職業生涯從未領過紅牌，紀錄完美無瑕。<br />\n當你看見球員為求接近勝利而無所不用其極：勾腳、拉衫、插水、佯傷、破口大罵..... 恩尼斯達卻從不節外生枝，不蓄意犯規，不傷害對手，不耍茅招博著數，以身作則說明堂堂正正一樣可以贏波。<br />\n恩尼斯達在領獎時說：「生命中有很多事都很重要，我不是想做一個典範，只想做得好，如果別人認為我做得不錯，那就更好了。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小白"},{"pid":"d619f76310bda55139d33fd8b2ab10598450616d","tid":507863,"uid":51951,"like":8,"dislike":32,"score":-24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T16:16:14.000Z","msg":"球技，球品，獎項都比唔上牙朗"},{"pid":"904d2481b4ac6886cf49175aa8eb133a7e1eb54a","tid":507863,"uid":120852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T16:18:12.000Z","msg":"覺得佢先係新類型球王<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa1cdbff8939eb638eba01489103b349df7ac11","tid":507863,"uid":120852,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"d619f76310bda55139d33fd8b2ab10598450616d","tid":507863,"uid":51951,"like":8,"dislike":32,"score":-24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T16:16:14.000Z","msg":"球技，球品，獎項都比唔上牙朗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T16:18:35.000Z","msg":"ching真幽默<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a59a3ece0958ab22adf42e179e6f1c5abd8b7a3","tid":507863,"uid":120852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T16:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92650fe2214b2bd7d3a6589b5103510868e2b135","tid":507863,"uid":120852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T16:43:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67e4afc6f596ef00998a94709d3a40f966b52b6d","tid":507863,"uid":68375,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T16:52:15.000Z","msg":"盤扭黎講同美斯同級"},{"pid":"789166701c2f58a0ff02d50eb7857f25739f6b6b","tid":507863,"uid":52087,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T16:53:06.000Z","msg":"其實佢唔差過拖舟<br />\n只係同隊個人榮譽喺晒美斯度"},{"pid":"7c6eebfefd884bb0a9842264cb9dc474b3f9de0c","tid":507863,"